features: Colorful Transparent Envelopes & Large Capacity: 5 assorted colors: transparent blue, green, yellow, purple, and pink (each color with 2). It's easy to organize and distinguish your paper with a different color. The envelope folder size is 13.25 x 9.25 inches, suitable for A4/US letter size files & other small items, holds no less than 200 sheets of paper.
Premium Quality & Waterproof: Durable PP material plastic and waterproof envelope folder with upgraded thickness to prevent tearing for durable using and holding your documents or other items safe.

Safe Paste Closure & Label Pocket: High-quality translucent document bag with safe paste closure, easy and convenient to take and store lightweight things, and durable to last long after multiple repeats. Plastic Envelopes have a pocket for labels to distinguish documents easily.
Transparent Document Pouches: The see-through sleek document folder keeps contents visible and makes finding documents so easy without opening your envelopes.

Easy Storage: Our plastic pouch is portable to keep your items organized and help you sort the clutter, the envelopes bags can be used at school, home, work, office, travel, and business trip. Outside mini label pocket helps classify and identify your document easily.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Very happy with these folders since I purchase many PDF patterns and now I can store them just perfectly in these folders. They are letter sized, have an Info tag on the front and just the greatest idea for my patterns. I bought 2 pkgs and now my sewing room is organized. I certainly will tell all my sewing buddies about these, good quality and great price, too.
